{"tid":2191533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"尷尬！國民黨歷任黨主席排齒輪喊話「轉動台灣」 結果卻互卡...","createTime":"2020-09-06T13:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T14:29:57.000Z","uid":199540,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a197c7f66b16d3925d3e424f26d29281d065bae1","tid":2191533,"uid":199540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-06/461397\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-09-06%2F461397&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4hyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=2a9b17bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-09-06/461397</a><br />\n<br />\n個齒輪係咪有d似曾相識呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yHPk1g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yHPk1g.jpg&h=3bda3d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國民黨今（6日）召開全國代表大會，國民黨大老、要角齊聚，但在歷任黨主席上台喊話要轉動台灣後，卻出現了意外的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n在國民黨全代會開場後的橋段當中，歷任黨主席馬英九、吳伯雄、朱立倫、洪秀柱、吳敦義，以及現任黨主席江啟臣上台，手拿著齒輪，喊話要世代傳承，轉動台灣。<br />\n<br />\n當六人皆將齒輪放上台灣地圖後，因其中四個齒輪緊密連接，按照此排列方式，將使齒輪出現完全無法轉動的窘境，但在一旁的投影動畫，因齒輪之間並無緊密相連，則仍可如常運轉。<br />\n<br />\n此不合機械原理的畫面一出，民進黨立委王定宇諷刺，齒輪這樣排列只會卡死，就如同中國國民黨決定繼續擁抱虛幻的「九二一中」。<br />\n<br />\n齒輪互卡的狀況，在今年六月中共黨媒人民日報透過臉書發佈「港區國安法為香港經濟撐腰」的宣傳圖片亦曾出現，以三個齒輪解析港版國安法對於香港經濟的重要性時，也被發現，只要最大齒輪「港版國安法」加進來，將使原本的兩個齒輪無法轉動。"},{"pid":"f266e685ae80132c8aa6591882ee773ff2244400","tid":2191533,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58502f7a7b0cf591c6979e8d4da026e3bf2acf8f","tid":2191533,"uid":49018,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"成個黨都係弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f43581c02fe744d25a1ab93a164b27395449fab","tid":2191533,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:37:39.000Z","msg":"同共匪如出一轍"},{"pid":"4d4ffd50689fe10ee82ac0b7e913499bf038cc40","tid":2191533,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日一柒"},{"pid":"081bad1dd87c0b70af559be41bcf06466fcb2cf1","tid":2191533,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:41:12.000Z","msg":"跟本係共匪文宣,&nbsp;無學精過.&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12a2a3c536f1ad70d0d18b50eb21aedfcf541a5","tid":2191533,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:43:36.000Z","msg":"有片想睇"},{"pid":"ffc52dcc322c02842eb6f4f60e46a013bc806e3d","tid":2191533,"uid":69289,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:44:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L7VKe9S.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL7VKe9S.gif&h=65f094e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民日報三齒輪國安法gif流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2073452\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2073452</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"79c08bd2f70a781307b806929514dd47a8d119e5","tid":2191533,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"國民黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7c88a474eb776a30bd9dd826dfbdda04b832d4","tid":2191533,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T13:47:39.000Z","msg":"同源編導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class